entry.title: Combined summary - Bitcoin Knots 23.0.knots20220529 released
entry.summary: Bitcoin Knots has released version 23.0.knots20220529 with new features, bug fixes, performance improvements, and updated translations. Users can find the release notes and change log on GitHub and report any bugs using the issue tracker available on GitHub. To stay updated with security and update notifications, users can subscribe to the announcements mailing list on the Bitcoin Knots website. The new version is available for download from the official website.
